50|$|The {{second section}} of the Northern <b>Busway,</b> {{also known as the}} Inner Northern <b>Busway,</b> officially opened on 19 May 2008. This section connects the first {{section of the}} Northern <b>Busway</b> to the South East <b>Busway</b> with {{stations}} at King George Square and Roma Street. To make room for the Inner Northern <b>Busway,</b> one rail platform at Roma Street railway station was removed.|$|R
