25|$|Metro Busway is {{an express}} bus system with {{characteristics}} of {{bus rapid transit}} with two lines operating on dedicated or shared-use <b>busways.</b> The system runs a total of 40 miles, with 27 stations and over 38,000 daily weekday boardings as of February 2012.|$|E
